name: Nocha the Kat
description: NOCHA the white cat of the KASPA gem invites to a world where magic and technology intertwine. With this adventure, the project aim to raise awareness of the Kaspa ecosystem and contribute to its expansion. NOCHA is a fair launch project powered by KRC20 Protocol with a community-driven vision. As a memecoin of the Kaspa blockchain, NOCHA is both a humorous and serious work to spread the knowledge of KASPA technology.
